    "updated_at": "2012-03-08T08:35:02Z",
    "body": "Rust has modules `core::os` and `core::path`.\nWhere would people expect to find a function to get the home directory?\nThe homedir is OS-specific, but it is also a path.\n\nPython has \"os.path.expanduser()\"\nRuby has \"File.expand_path()\"\nHaskell has \"System.Directory.getHomeDirectory\".\n",
